Kareem Sasa

Who am I?

I spend the majority of my time now improving my technical web development skills. This includes taking on independent projects, collaborating with other individuals interested in software development, as well as contributing to open source projects.

About This Site

This website was initially developed in the spring of 2021.

The main purposes of this website are listed here:

  • Discuss the interesting aspects and technical details regarding computer science, cyber security, and software engineering

  • Document the implementation of solutions to real problems

  • Present my independent research projects

  • Record my personal achievements

It should be noted that all the contents of this website are solely my own, and do not express the views or opinions of any employer.

Contact Me

If you have any questions regarding my Github open source projects, please open an issue ticket in the repository. For private questions, please contact me via my personal email.
